INSERT INTO `nge_icl_strings` VALUES('5503', 'en', 'page-builder-shortcode-strings-634', '9ff39a0e164d96e2b16b9e2720cff61b', '\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Importance of Time Management</strong></h1>\r\nTime is one of the most valuable assets we have, and everyone has the same amount, whether you are a millionaire or an executive of a large corporation you still only have 24 hours a day just like everybody.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis means that if you can utilise your time better you have an automatic advantage over other people and can achieve more, be more relaxed and be able to spend more time with the people most important to you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTo be able to be better at time management it is important to understand why it is so valuable. Here are 3 reasons why time management is crucial to your success and well-being:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Better results with less effort</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWhen you really master time management, you improve your ability to focusing on a task. When you can really focus on a task and not get distracted with Facebook, emails, chats, or other distractions you can achieve an astonishing amount of work in a short amount of time. The result? Improved results, with much less effort.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n 	<li>Better Decision making</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWhen you are able to manage your time effectively, your stress levels are reduced significantly. No more thinking, I need to thisâ¦ I need to do thatâ¦. With great time management, you know what needs to be done and know how to focus on getting it done. Without getting too technical, no matter how logical we think our decisions are, every decision we make has an emotional component to it. When we have less stress, we are able to make clearer decisions as our emotions are more stable. For more information about decision making and emotions you can read Thinking Fast and Slow by Daniel Kahneman.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li>More time with family &amp; friends</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nLastly, with better time management you are able to spend more time with your family and friends and doing activities that you enjoy. Better time management means less time working as you are able to achieve more in less time, this means you are able to switch off and spend more time playing sport, relaxing and spending time with the people most important to you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nListen to Sreypov (above) talk about how improving her time management has helped her business.', '17', '1', '', 'VISUAL', 'vc_column_text: content', '0', '', 'c33d8fb65d8db2cf661e8465aa8c2979', 'optional', '378');
